|       4 | header  |
|       8 | header  |
|---------+---------|
| replace | replace |
"
   "
|  2 | header |
|  4 | header |
|  8 | header |
|----+--------|
| 14 | 28     |
"
   2
   ;; Calc formula
   "#+TBLFM: @>$1 = vsum(@<..@>>) :: $2 = 2 * $1"
   ;; Lisp formula
   "#+TBLFM: @>$1 = '(+ @<..@>>); N :: $2 = '(* 2 $1); N"))

